Cash flow traps often start small and stay hidden until the damage is visible.  
But once you know what to watch for, you can **stay proactive, protect your margins, and stabilize growth**.

Whether youâ€™re preventing future issues or fixing current ones, success comes from tracking data closely and making decisions based on **cash flow realityâ€”not just profit on paper**.

